run the cutter
Homonym Number:
Word Class: phrase
Sense Number:
Definition:to procure beer in a vessel (poss. orig. on the sly) for drinking off the licensed premises, often after hours.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
